Product Version     25.10    Cadence Design Systems, Inc.
report_parameter(25.10)                                report_parameter(25.10)

Name
       report_parameter  - Generates a report showing define_parameter command
       settings

Syntax
       report_parameter

        [-help]

        [-correlation]

        [-name <string>]

       Generates a report showing define_parameter command settings.

Parameters
       -help  Prints out the command usage.

       -correlation
              Reports the parameter correlation.

       -name <<string>>
              Reports the parameter name.

       -scope {vtskew | wire_variation

               | beol | lle layout_effect}" Reports the parameter  scope.  Al-
              lowed options are:

              * vtskew

              * wire_variation

              * beol

              * lle layout_effect

       -view <<string>>
              Shows the name of the specified view name.

Examples
              *

                The  following command reports moments information of M2 layer
                resistance:

                define_parameter -name param_M2_R -scope wire_variation  -dis-
                tribution gaussian -range {1, 1.15}

                report_parameter -scope wire_variation -view func_spg_m4c_cmax

                -----------------------------------------------------------------------

                                    PARAMETERS ( SCOPE: wire_variation )

                -----------------------------------------------------------------------

                Name         Mean-shift    Std-dev     Distribution     Analy-
                sis Type

                -----------------------------------------------------------------------

                param_M2_R   0.075         0.025       Normal           Setup

                param_M2_R   0.075         0.025       Normal           Hold

                -----------------------------------------------------------------------

Related Information
              * define_parameter

              * set_wire_variation_mode

              * get_wire_variation_mode

Related Information
              * For  more information, refer to "Wire Variation Analysis" sec-
                tion in the Innovus User Guide.

